{"tid":620694,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"由細到大的夢想就係做公務員，係味無大志。","createTime":"2018-04-07T17:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T11:11:58.000Z","uid":2467,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"33141a0cdc79d1ece1034a4b8b7b1795ffde5252","tid":620694,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T17:47:51.000Z","msg":"成日比女朋友笑無大志。忽發奇想，係到諗呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解我由細到大對其他工無咩興趣，淨係諗過做政務官或者做個好警察，屋企唔等我開飯。<br />\n<br />\n入到大學，有諗過做老師，但番母校教下補習班之後發現，如果唔係教高中，我真係唔會教得落手，我一路教就一路覺得我成個補習名師咁，唔係好理學生，一味教佢地點拆題目。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，中小學老師唔係淨係教學術，係要教埋學生品德，我無咁的信心。<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人係咁。今年yr3了，開始諗搵工，無從入手，再係咁，如無意外真係考份公務員工就算，但就會比人笑無大志。"},{"pid":"70a91fc87f9bb7e617b0d3e770a4932d42891cb0","tid":620694,"uid":50162,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T17:49:12.000Z","msg":"你入到先算啦，唔知衰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87d7019642ee7f481240bd2d46d98613c653d1e","tid":620694,"uid":179527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77d1d09c743fe36d557e6ac13b53dc701585a702","tid":620694,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70a91fc87f9bb7e617b0d3e770a4932d42891cb0","tid":620694,"uid":50162,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T17:49:12.000Z","msg":"你入到先算啦，唔知衰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T17:50:34.000Z","msg":"到入到先黎開post咩"},{"pid":"a2a384415a546550c1c62c9b18cad5ad3e6b27df","tid":620694,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c87d7019642ee7f481240bd2d46d98613c653d1e","tid":620694,"uid":179527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T17:49:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"唔愁米飯<br />\n<br />\n正正常常